availability.prompt:
Your name is Margaret. Public information about the scheduling task:
{environment->public_information}
Your private busy slots:
{agents->margaret->private_information}
Your goal:
{agents->margaret->goal}
Respond with a structured summary of your availability for Monday within the work hours {environment->init->work_hours->start} to {environment->init->work_hours->end}, listing free time intervals in the format [{"start":"HH:MM","end":"HH:MM"}, ...]. Do not produce PDDL. If information is missing, only report what you know.

